import React from 'react';
import {Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Link, IconButton} from '@mui/material';
import {Facebook, YouTube, Instagram} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <Box sx = {{ backgroundColor: '#842c6a', color: 'white', padding: '20px 0px'}}>
            <Container maxWidth = 'lg'>
                <Grid container spacing = {4}>
                    <Grid item xs = {12} md = {4} sx = {{textAlign: {xs: 'center', md: 'left'} }}>
                        <Box sx = {{display: 'flex', justifyContent: {xs: 'center', md: 'left'} }}>
                            <IconButton href = "#" color = "inherit" aria-label  = "Facebook">
                                <Facebook/>
                            </IconButton>
                            <IconButton href = "#" color = "inherit" aria-label  = "YouTube">
                                <YouTube/>
                            </IconButton>
                            <IconButton href = "#" color = "inherit" aria-label  = "Instagram">
                                <Instagram/>
                            </IconButton>
                        </Box>
                        <Typography variant = "body2"> Follow Us on Social Media</Typography>
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid item xs={12} md={2}>
                        <Typography variant ="h6" sx={{fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Service</Typography>
                        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline ="none">
                            <Typography variant = "body2"> Music & Performance</Typography>
                        </Link>
                        <Link href ="#" color="inherit" underline ="none">
                            <Typography variant = "body2">Party Essentials</Typography>
                        </Link>
                        <Link href ="#" color="inherit" underline ="none">
                            <Typography variant = "body2">Interactive Experiences</Typography>
                        </Link>
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid item xs={12} md={2}>
                        <Typography variant ="h6" sx={{fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Costumer Service</Typography>
                        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="none">
                            <Typography variant="body2">Terms of Service</Typography>
                        </Link>
                        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="none">
                            <Typography variant="body2">Privacy Policy</Typography>
                        </Link>
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid item xs={12} md={2}>
                        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Are You A Vendor?</Typography>
                        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="none">
                            <Typography variant="body2">Accesibility</Typography>
                        </Link>
                        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="none">
                            <Typography variant="body2">About Us</Typography>
                        </Link>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>

                <Box sx={{textAlign: 'center', marginTop:'20px'}}>
                    <Typography variant="body2">© 2024 MiTiara</Typography>
                </Box>
            </Container>
        </Box>
    );
};

export default Footer;
